Name: Basic Ragnr Rune
Types: Rune
Components: Runestone, Strength 13 Or Greater
Description: This rune symbolizes destruction and chaos, allowing those who channel it to tap into the power of destruction.SPACESPACEWhile wearing or using an item imbued with this rune, you gain the following feature.SPACECorruptionSPACEAs an action, you can lash out at a creature with destructive energy. Make a melee spell attack against a creature within your reach. On a hit, the target takes POTENCY1-3POTENCYd8 necrotic damage and has disadvantage on the next ability check or saving throw it makes before the end of your next turn.SPACESPACEYou may use this rune a number of times equal to your proficiency bonus before its magic is depleted. The rune will recharge from ambient magic as you complete a long rest.
